  "text": "After the relevant heuristics were identified, 18 screen shots of WebCIS Web pages were captured. These Web pages represented observed information needs events from our previous study. Subsequently, these screen shots were modified so that they contained links to information resources accessed using infobuttons and the Infobutton Manager [CITATION_1] . The screen shots were collated into a booklet, along with 14 other screen shots, showing typical Web pages that could be viewed by a WebCIS user. The evaluators were also given a narrative describing the user interacting with WebCIS as he or she accessed various components of the system-this was done to provide the evaluator with a context as they reviewed the screen shots.",
  "correct_citation": {
